  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nIt's hard to collect logs detailed enough to analyze emerging issues due to the high storage requirement. \r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nAllow to manually temporary raise log level with per-class granularity via CLI.\r\nCollect future logs(or the past ones too if possible)\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nCollect complete logs all the time - too much space required\r\nCollect complete logs by changing logs settings - prevents from catching runtime problems which disappear after a restart\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nIt might be cool to trigger from the code also when some weird stuff is detected, disabled by default.\r\n",
